<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• شفَر الشَّيءَ:</span> أصاب حرفَه <span class="c1">"شفَر الإناءَ"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>